            <title><![CDATA[【图集】李登辉移灵安葬 蔡英文灵前献花]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media figure-media-gallery figure-media-gallery-overlay js-figure-media-gallery js-figure-media-gallery-overlay"> <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202010/20201007/file7cndvte8fnr12j3y833e.jpg?itok=B4jQnF26" alt data-caption="蔡英文向李登辉灵前献花并三鞠躬。（路透社）" src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202010/20201007/file7cndvte8fnr12j3y833e.jpg?itok=B4jQnF26" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div><figcaption><p>蔡英文向李登辉灵前献花并三鞠躬。（路透社）</p></figcaption></div> <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202010/20201007/file7cndvcoxyioxiu7m6xn.jpg?itok=Sn0ugSH2" alt data-caption="移灵车队抵达公墓后，李登辉孙女婿赵赞凯手捧遗像进入墓区。（路透社）" src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202010/20201007/file7cndvcoxyioxiu7m6xn.jpg?itok=Sn0ugSH2" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div><figcaption><p>移灵车队抵达公墓后，李登辉孙女婿赵赞凯手捧遗像进入墓区。（路透社）</p></figcaption></div> <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202010/20201007/file7cndvt9a6lc5frwsb5q.jpg?itok=BVRZVJTM" alt data-caption="葬枪班鸣放葬枪三响，表达对李登辉崇敬与追思。（路透社）" src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202010/20201007/file7cndvt9a6lc5frwsb5q.jpg?itok=BVRZVJTM" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div><figcaption><p>葬枪班鸣放葬枪三响，表达对李登辉崇敬与追思。（路透社）</p></figcaption></div><div class="figure-media-gallery-nav"></div></div>

<p>已故台湾前总统李登辉的奉安礼拜活动今早（7日）在新北市五指山国军示范公墓举行。台湾总统蔡英文率副总统赖清德等政府官员出席礼拜仪式，李登辉长眠于该公墓特勋区。</p>

<p>据台湾《联合报》报道，李登辉7月30日在台北荣总医院病逝，享年98岁。今天举行奉安礼拜，全台公务机关下半旗一天。</p>

<p>李登辉家属与蔡英文、赖清德、总统府秘书长李大维、总统府副秘书长李俊俋、内政部长徐国勇、国防部副部长张哲平等人出席礼拜仪式，仪式历时一小时。</p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1-wrapper" class="dfp-tag-wrapper">
<div id="dfp-ad-imu1" class="dfp-tag-wrapper">
      
</div>
</div></section>

<p>移灵车队今早从李登辉生前所住的翠山庄出发。车队抵达五指山国军示范公墓后，由孙女李坤仪手捧李登辉骨灰坛、李坤仪丈夫赵赞凯手捧李登辉遗像进入墓区。</p>

<p>蔡英文、赖清德等随后均进行了礼敬仪式，结束后，由台湾基督长老教会举行礼拜，礼拜程序后行奉安礼，在国防部鸣葬枪3响以及号兵司安息号后圆满礼成，歷时约近2小时。</p>

<p>反台独团体“蓝天行动联盟”、“333联盟”以及“拔菜总部”等今天也到场进行抗议，在车队经过的马路口举旗呐喊表达诉求，约上午10时许团队准备离场，但因地处管制区，警方围起“人墙”阻挡队伍离场，场面火爆一度爆发推挤冲突。</p>

